			    (edge-type STRING) 
			    (target GRAPH-VERTEX)
			    (graph GRAPH))
  "Returns link object from <source> vertex to <target-vertex> with
   name <edge-type>, else nil."
  (find-graph-edge source (util::safe-word-to-symbol edge-type) target graph))

